# MAINTAINERS

This file lists the maintainers responsible for reviewing plugin submissions.

## Active Maintainers

| GitHub Username | Role          |
|-----------------|---------------|
| MorCherlf       | Lead Maintainer |

## Review Policy

- All plugin submissions require at least **1 Maintainer approval** before merging.
- PRs that introduce unapproved auxiliary images require **extra scrutiny** of the image source, Dockerfile, and publisher reputation.
- Even GriffinGuard team members must submit plugins through this repository. There are no exceptions.

## Becoming a Maintainer

Maintainers are appointed by the Lead Maintainer based on sustained contributions and demonstrated understanding of the plugin security model.
